{
  "stem": "8527.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was easier for her to do it because as a child, as a young girl, if you didn't look Jewish nobody bothered you.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But as a boy, it was much more difficult because of the circumcision.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All they have to do is take your pants down, they knew you were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because in Poland nobody was circumcised in those years.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So she was more involved with the business than-- than I, helping out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I also remember the black market.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the gendarmes used to come in and-- in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there was one guy by the name of Lolek, never forget him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was a Polish national that lived on the German border.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were called, I believe, Volksdeutchen, and he was in the gendarmes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one day, he came to the house, dragged my dad out of bed about 2:00, 3:00 in the morning.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in  a hallway-- they used to have like a two-by-four to guard doors.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he took that two-by-four and proceeded to beat my dad with it, broke his arm.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because he didn't pay off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Somebody squealed on him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That I do remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I remember my dad walking around with the sling on him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I felt-- I-- I felt-- I felt terrible for my dad.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I've always felt extreme compassion for my father.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He represented something very soft and very idealistic and so on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not so my mother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My mother was more the pusher and shover and so on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it was a different relationship, always.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "All these years, I still picture him the same way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I remember one time he had to have a tooth pulled, and there was no such thing as Novocaine or whatever.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So he didn't go to the shop that day.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
